OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776265867
OL,3,CTeenager charged in connection with
OL,4,Cmurder after man stabbed in Primrose
OL,5,CHill
OL,7,FA teenager has been charged in
OL,8,Fconnection with murder after a 21-year-
OL,9,Fold man was killed in Primrose Hill in
OL,10,FCamden.
OL,12,FFinbar Sullivan was fatally stabbed in
OL,13,Fa fight which broke out in the north
OL,14,FLondon park on April 9.
OL,16,FOfficers have been examining footage
OL,17,Fcirculating online which appears to
OL,18,Fshow the moments leading up to the
OL,19,Fstabbing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
