OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776265867
OL,3,CTeenager charged in connection with
OL,4,Cmurder after man stabbed in Primrose
OL,5,CHill
OL,7,FA second man, aged in his 20s, was
OL,8,Ffound nearby in Regent's Park Road
OL,9,Fwith knife wounds and was taken to
OL,10,Fhospital.
OL,12,FKhalid Abdulqadir, 18, of Fellows
OL,13,FRoad, Camden, has been charged with
OL,14,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent,
OL,15,Fviolent disorder and possession of a
OL,16,Fknife.
OL,18,FHe was arrested on Sunday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
