OL,3,CTeenager charged in connection with
OL,4,Cmurder after man stabbed in Primrose
OL,5,CHill
OL,7,FAnother man, Oliuwadamilola
OL,8,FOgunyankinnu, 27 of Southbury Road,
OL,9,FEnfield, was charged with murder on
OL,10,FSunday after being arrested on Friday,
OL,11,F10 April.
OL,13,FHe appeared at Stratford Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt yesterday.
OL,16,FA 25-year-man, who was arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender,
OL,18,Fwas released with no further action.
OL,20,FThe investigation is ongoing.
